videos.description: Washington's Kelsey Plum sinks the lefty floater to surpass Jackie Stiles for the most points in NCAA women's basketball history. The basket also gave Plum 55 points for the game against Utah.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Plum becomes NCAA women's all-time leading scorer) 2017/02/25
